name: CdhMetaverse Token
description: CDH Metaverse is a virtual meta space + NFT ecological network based on blockchain, which is initiated by cdhm foundation. Its vision is to build a next-generation virtual + reality ecological interconnected meta universe. It combines a series of advanced technologies such as blockchain, XR (Ar + VR + MR) and decentralized finance, aiming to bring users better virtual reality experience and economic incentive effect.
